\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_(United_Kingdom)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The National Lottery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_(United_Kingdom)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_(United_Kingdom)\"}, {\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"score\": 0.9999435662236122, \"rank\": 3.283459500594177e-05, \"text\": \"Grainger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\"}, {\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles 2028\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the different sports\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"a very different model\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former rower Grainger, who competed at five Olympics, winning one gold and four silver medals, told the PA news agency: \\\"There is an absolute assumption by everyone, understandably, that funding is decided on the back of results.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"score\": 0.9999435662236122, \"rank\": 3.283459500594177e-05, \"text\": \"Grainger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five Olympics\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"one gold\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"four silver medals\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"an absolute assumption\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Almost like you will be rewarded if you do well and punished if you do not do well.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a very different model of investment now.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very different model\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the sports have been told a suggested amount already, pre-Games.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the sports\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"a suggested amount\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"Games\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So the results in Paris are of use and of interest, but will not be directly affecting the funding going forward.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999726981063, \"rank\": 2.7301939737554054e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"the funding\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all about future potential.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"future potential\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So even if a sport wasn't successful at these Games, if the conversation has been had, that actually in LA it could be successful for a very good reason, then the finances will be secured.\\\"\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"a very good reason\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"the finances\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB's medals tally was spread across 18 different sports and Grainger said UK Sport's strategy was \\\"very much aimed at the breadth of sport\\\".\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999963326055369, \"rank\": 3.6628183168439356e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"score\": 0.9999435662236122, \"rank\": 3.283459500594177e-05, \"text\": \"Grainger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\"}, {\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"18 different sports\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"the breadth\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is an argument that if you go narrower and just focus on a few sports, you can be very successful and some nations do that very well,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an argument\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"a few sports\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"some nations\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We feel we have got a responsibility to go for as wide a range as we can.\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a responsibility\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's more of interest to the public - you get more support from the public.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"more support\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is public investment, it's lottery money and Exchequer money and it needs to go as far as it can.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2147, \"end\": 2156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exchequer\", \"score\": 0.9401267799576916, \"rank\": 0.06368508654629937, \"text\": \"Exchequer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exchequer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exchequer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public investment\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"lottery money\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not everyone will relate to every sport, but if you have got 18 sports that you are successful in, there is something for everyone in that family of sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not everyone\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"every sport\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"18 sports\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"that family\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2347}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grainger said UK Sport had targeted between 50 and 70 medals and a top-five finish in the overall table and described Team GB's haul as \\\"a huge success\\\".\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2361, \"end\": 2369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"score\": 0.9999435662236122, \"rank\": 3.283459500594177e-05, \"text\": \"Grainger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\"}, {\"begin\": 2375, \"end\": 2383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999963326055369, \"rank\": 3.6628183168439356e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"50 and 70 medals\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"a top-five finish\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall table\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge success\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One or two gold medals can be the difference between where you finish - that's why it's not the real target for us,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One or two gold medals\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"the difference\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"the real target\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The real aim is the breadth of medals.\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The real aim\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"the breadth\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sixty-five medals, normally when you get that you are in the top five, so it's quite an unusual Games that we have not made it into the top five.\\\"\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite an unusual Games\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grainger was speaking at a National Lottery 'ChangeMaker' event at North Paddington Youth Club in London, where she was joined by Team GB medal winners Noah Williams (diving), Lewis Richardson (boxing), Lola Anderson (rowing) and Joe Clarke (kayak).\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 3083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"score\": 0.9999435662236122, \"rank\": 3.283459500594177e-05, \"text\": \"Grainger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K